\n<br />\nAnd echoes in the world of freedom.<br />\n<br />\nI turn my wear to the dark and black.<br />\n<br />\nAnd the mission <br />\nthat was planted in my brain<br />\nStill remains."},{"pid":"8c7ffbaa127d774c4584d847d18706ae4a88e1ac","tid":1296764,"uid":46534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T02:55:52.000Z","msg":"［文宣組入］文宣都要勇武<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1313774\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1313774</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2db8445479eba73900ad3e96a64e57b101152bdb","tid":1296764,"uid":23023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T02:58:03.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n背囊咁平都有既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec8bf5d564bf0f2751825a1b740500b2b7de6bcc","tid":1296764,"uid":269009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2572738133c8150c528e6135872f398bfb355ed","tid":1296764,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T12:53:03.000Z","msg":"首先<br />\n本人極力譴責示威及衝擊警方行為<br />\n故此希望同一眾連登藍絲鑽研Black Bloc戰術<br />\n以制衡黃絲暴徒<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Black Bloc<br />\n</strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">目的</span></strong><br />\n1. 減少個人表面特徵，從而減低被入罪風險<br />\n2. 愈多人Black Bloc，警方跟蹤及鎖定愈難<br />\n3. 隨處都係天眼<br />\n<br />\n遮掩部位<br />\n1. 臉<br />\n2. 耳<br />\n3. 髮型<br />\n4. 眼及眉 (如可最好)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">例子</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yQ9HUWw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyQ9HUWw.png&h=b2961332&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kMrnUWx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkMrnUWx.png&h=ed0fb014&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LUFcxJd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLUFcxJd.png&h=bb215ee5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">裝備</span></strong><br />\n口罩<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ab26B96.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAb26B96.png&h=f988177e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n各大藥房及化妝品店有售<br />\n<br />\n黑色帽<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sveMCap.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsveMCap.png&h=9bd47e25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nMiniso $29<br />\nH&amp;M $39<br />\n<br />\n頭巾<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4pSROhO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4pSROhO.png&h=332d4824&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n包頭包面皆可<br />\nDecathlon $19<br />\n深水埗特賣場 $5<br />\n<br />\n雨褸<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oGYNmDd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoGYNmDd.png&h=e4be3114&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nDecathlon $169<br />\n<br />\n背囊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5fqgeYm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5fqgeYm.png&h=cd9150cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nDecathlon $19<br />\n尋日已經見到有人用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有帽衛衣<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kSKs55w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkSKs55w.png&h=355e20d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黑超 (反光鏡)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z2gGq6b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz2gGq6b.png&h=0289f4af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n基本要求：<br />\n帽+口罩+頭巾<br />\n<br />\n尋日已經見到多人用頭巾<br />\n但大眾保護意識仲係太低<br />\n<br />\n記住<br />\n口罩已經唔足夠！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T03:00:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a21907fb3d7fbbcee2003af48d6182aef7d0a565","tid":1296764,"uid":125857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T03:00:49.000Z","msg":"琴晚買咗 見到好多兄弟買裝備"},{"pid":"c7c2fb44eb90629b52815213217ee2c0df901106","tid":1296764,"uid":93350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T03:06:0